  "title": "Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description & Requirements</strong><br /><br />· Actively seek out new sales opportunities by identifying and targeting potential customers in the enterprise software market, with a preference for those needing Edutech and Office Automation (OA) systems solution.</p><p>· Stay informed about software industry trends, competitive services, and market conditions.</p><p>· Create and deliver persuasive sales presentations and proposals to potential customers.</p><p>· Build and maintain strong relationships with existing/new clients to understand their evolving needs, address concerns, and ensure client satisfaction.<br /></p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><p>· Degree or above in Marketing, Business Administration or related</p><p>· 2 years or more of B2B software sales experience, with a proven track record of meeting or surpassing sales targets. Prior sales experience in the Edutech and OA office software industry is desirable.</p><p>· Excellent communication and interpersonal skills.</p><p>· Ability to work independently and as part of a team.</p><p>· Must maintain high professional and technical knowledge standard.</p><p>· Fluency in English and Chinese to interactions with Mandarin-speaking clients or staff at the China branch.</p>",
